	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Removing a game menu need help</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Might be a bus conflict, which most emulators don't handle correctly. Not even Nintendulator from my experiences. You might want to see how your mapper handles CHR bank switching and see how the hack behaves when you enter that menu. That would probably be easier than trying to remove the entire menu.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


